title: Pat Benatar 35th Anniversary Tour Album 2015 320ak
description:
Together, Pat Benatar and Neil Giraldo have sold more than 25 million albums, winning four Grammy Awards and three American Music Awards along the way. 
The duo's 19 Top 40 singles include unforgettable hits such as "Love Is a Battlefield," "Hit Me With Your Best Shot", "Promises In The Dark" and "Heartbreaker."
